Shaun Andrew McKerry tried to rob a post office in County Durham with an axe . 
  He was jumped on by shopkeeper Sab Dhillon and wrestled to the floor . 
  His wife Sam then hit him with a baseball bat to disarm him . 
  McKerry was jailed for six years after pleading guilty to attempted robbery . 
  The 31-year-old was dubbed Boomerang Boy or Homing Pigeon Boy in his youth . 
 